  "texts": [
    "Our primary goal is to facilitate more accurate detection of toxicity, thereby alleviating the issue of false positive misjudgments and protecting freedom of speech, which aims to contribute to the creation of a more harmonious online environment.",
    "We construct a meta-toxic knowledge graph filled with toxic content.",
    "However, there is also a risk of potential misuse of our proposed method.",
    "Specifically, our methods might be misused to generate toxic speech.",
    "It is essential to emphasize that our work focuses on detecting toxic speech while safeguarding freedom of speech, instead of censorship."
  ],
